---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 首頁
---

<div class="mb-12">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">FW Blog</h1>
  <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">分享 Web 開發和技術的心得</p>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">最新文章</h2>

<div class="space-y-6">
{% for post in collections.posts | limit(10) %}
  {% include "components/post-card.njk" %}
{% endfor %}
</div>

{% if collections.posts.length == 0 %}
<div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
  <p class="text-blue-800">目前還沒有任何文章。開始撰寫您的第一篇文章吧！</p>
</div>
{% endif %}
